  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"single-post\"\u003e\n                                    \n                \u003cp\u003eNews outlets tend to highlight the first 100 days of a new administration, and they like to show the changes with charts. It gives a feel for a true direction instead of empty claims and where we might be headed for the next few years. This time around was no exception.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor Bloomberg, Mark Niquette and Gregory Korte \u003ca href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-04-30/trump-scorecard-charting-his-first-100-days-in-office?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzb3VyY2UiOiJTdWJzY3JpYmVyR2lmdGVkQXJ0aWNsZSIsImlhdCI6MTc0NjAzNDA2OCwiZXhwIjoxNzQ2NjM4ODY4LCJhcnRpY2xlSWQiOiJTVkpET05EV1gyUFMwMCIsImJjb25uZWN0SWQiOiIzRDhGMEEzMTc2MDc0NUM5OTg4NkFCNzA1NDk2RUNEQSJ9.wZ0o0m8UFf85xm_dTN8ESe2VB0mmDR7F-NUS1pOr9B8\"\u003echarted the economy\u003c/a\u003e, which is complex and can’t be shown with a single metric, so they showed several, such as inflation expectations:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"78412\" data-permalink=\"https://flowingdata.com/2025/04/30/charts-for-trumps-first-100-days/trump-scorecard-bloomberg/\" data-orig-file=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg.png\" data-orig-size=\"1248,860\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"Trump scorecard bloomberg\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-750x517.png\" data-large-file=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-1090x751.png\" src=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-750x517.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"517\" srcset=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-750x517.png 750w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-1090x751.png 1090w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-210x145.png 210w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg-768x529.png 768w, https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Trump-scorecard-bloomberg.png 1248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor Axios, Jacque Schrag and Natalie Daher used a \u003ca href=\"https://www.axios.com/visuals/trump-presidency-100-days-timeline\"\u003etimeline of events\u003c/a\u003e, color coded by type:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"78416\" data-permalink=\"https://flowingdata.com/2025/04/30/charts-for-trumps-first-100-days/axios-100-days-events/\" data-orig-file=\"https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Axios-100-days-events.png\" data-orig-size=\"1378,1254\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#3